quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  87,16,Chɛli gba! Yi gahindila Dunia bɛhigu (ka chεri Chiyaama)
  87,17,"Chiyaama mi n-nyɛ din gari, ka nyɛ kpaliŋkpaa"
  87,18,Achiika! Ŋɔ maa be kurumbuni kundinima la puuni
  87,19,Annabi Ibrahima mini Annabi Musa kundinima
  88,1,"(Yaa nyini Annabi)! Di ni- bɔŋɔ, din liriti ninsalinim’ nina la (Chiyaama) lahibali ka a na"
  88,2,Dindali maa ka ninvuɣu shɛba nina yɛn ba tiŋgbani ni
  88,3,"Ka di nyɛla din yɛn ti tum tuunkpɛma, ka niŋ wahala (buɣum ni)"
  88,4,Di yɛn ti kpela buɣum tulli ni
  88,5,Ka bɛ nyuhiri ba kobilnina shɛli din nyɛ kotulum
  88,6,Bɛ ka bindirgu naɣila gabligɔhi
  88,7,"Di bi ŋmɛlinda (ninsalinima), di mi bi kuri kum"
  88,8,"Dindali maa, ninvuɣu shɛba nina polo yɛn ti mali suhupiɛlli"
  88,9,Ka bɛ tuma nyɛla bɛ ni saɣi ti shɛli
  88,10,Ka bɛ yɛn ti be Alizanda shɛli din du la ni
  88,11,A ku wum yɛltɔɣa kaha di (Alizanda maa) puuni
  88,12,Di puuni malila kobilnin’ shɛli din kuli zɔra
  88,13,Ka di puuni mali gar’ shɛŋa din duhi zuɣusaa
  88,14,"Ni dama dam kopu-nima, ka bɛ zaŋ zali bɛ tooni"
  88,15,Ni dufɛmeensi din pempe taba
  88,16,Ni bindɔhi din yɛrgi
  88,17,"Di ni bɔŋɔ, bɛ (ninsalinim’) bi lihiri bɛ (Naawuni) ni nam laakumi shɛm"
  88,18,Ka nya bɛ ni duhi sagbana shɛm
  88,19,Ka lihi bɛ ni kpamkpa zoya shɛm
  88,20,Ka lahi lihi bɛ ni yɛrgi tiŋgbani shɛm
  88,21,"Dinzuɣu (yaa nyini Annabi)! Niŋmi wa’azu, achiika! A nyɛla wa’azulana"
  88,22,A pala ŋun niŋdi ba talahi (ni dolsigu)
  88,23,"Naɣila ninvuɣu so ŋun lebi biri, ka niŋ chɛfuritali"
  88,24,Ka Naawuni niŋ o azaaba din galsi
  88,25,Achiika! Bɛ labbu shee nyɛla Ti (Tinim’ Naawuni) sani
  88,26,"Din nyaaŋa, Bɛ saliya bela Ti sani"